auto lo
iface lo inet loopback

auto enp4s0
iface enp4s0 inet static
    address 192.168.1.248/24
    gateway 192.168.1.1
    ethernet-wol g
iface enp5s0 inet manual
    ethernet-wol g
iface enp6s0 inet manual
    ethernet-wol g
iface enp7s0 inet manual
    ethernet-wol g

